THE MAIN WAY TO BEAT BOSSES<br>
is just to make sure ALL your aeons are on full overdrive before battle, that should do the trick...<br>
And make SURE you have gotten HASTEGA, i cannot stress this the most, that is one of the best spells you can ever get.  And if you find yourself taking too much damage, have Yuna cast PROTECT. <br>
<br>
oh yea, make sure you capture EVERYTHING... the arena guy gives you sooo much stuff<br>
<br>
This one's a CHEAP trick...<br>
Step 1 - Capture all things in the Thunder Plains for the Arena<br>
Step 2 - Put your desired Characters on COMRADE overdrive mode, Stoic if you dont have it<br>
Step 3 - Equip them with OVERDRIVE&gt;AP weapons(ESSENTIAL) , and x2-3 Overdrive/AP if you can<br>
Step 4 - BUY A TON OF PHOENIX DOWNS<br>
Step 5 - head to the Arena (Eastern Calm Lands)<br>
Step 6 - Challenge the CACTUAR KING<br>
-Now let him wail on you, and never ever attack. Pheonix as soon as anyone dies, and continually Triangle when everyone's alive. Let this go on and on...<br>
And if he doesn't run away, and you are about to run out of Down's, revive everyone and use the skill FLEE.<br>
<br>
And if you do this right...<br>
the award is LOTS AND LOTS O' S.LEVELS!!!<br>
i got 47 levels in 4 mins... nuff' sed  <br>
Since the king does either 10,000 or 99,999 dmg, it translates into 10k or 99k AP!!<br>
And if you add x3/2 Overdrive and/or AP imagine... you could get 899991 AP in ONE HIT<br>
(Make sure to do this with Yuna, as soon as you get Anima &amp; the Sisters, put her on Tidus's route, then onto Auron's. My Anima topped off with 236 Strength, and abnormally high Agility. I was doing 99,999dmg 3-6 times in a row...) <p>SLICEY SLICEY!!</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm31.showPrevMessage?topicID=6.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm31.showNextMessage?topicID=6.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm31.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm31.emailToFriend?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm31.threadControl?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm31.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm31.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub25.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="polykarbonbbsfrm18">PK-BBS Rules and Regulations!<option value="p